NK125(co)002:0: //'phags pa'i gnas brtan chen po bcu drug gi lo rgyus mdor bsdus bzhugs so //
NK125(co)002:1: ston pas bstan pa gtad cing mi rnams tshe lo
NK125(co)002:2: yar 'phel gyi bdun brgya thub pa'i bar du mya
NK125(co)002:3: ngan las mi 'da' bar sems can gyi don mdzad
NK125(co)002:4: cing rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'dzin skyong spel ba'i phyir
NK125(co)002:5: so so'i 'khor dgra bcom pa'i tshogs dang bcas te
NK125(co)002:6: gangs ti si sogs gnas so sor bzhugs pa yin
NK125(co)002:8: r+aa hu lah sgra gcan 'dzin ni rgyal bu don
NK125(co)002:9: 'grub dang grags 'dzin ma'i sras lo drug mngal du
NK125(co)002:10: bzhugs pa de nyid ma grags 'dzin ma dang lhan
NK125(co)002:11: cig pri yang ku'i gling na bzhugs par bshad /
NK125(co)002:13: yan lag 'byung ni khyim bdag bzang po'i chung ma bde ldan ma'i bu yin zhing /
NK125(co)002:14: sngar bcom ldan 'das kyis bu nyid du lung bstan
NK125(co)002:15: pa la mu stegs pa'i phrag dog gi tshig gis
NK125(co)002:16: rmongs par byas pas phas lto ba mnyes nas ma
NK125(co)002:17: shi ba'i ro dur khrod bsil ba tshal du bsreg
NK125(co)002:18: pa'i lto ba nas pad+ma dang bcas te skyes pa
NK125(co)002:19: me skyes zhes grags pa de dgra bcom thob pa
NK125(co)002:20: nyid yin no // a dzi tah mi pham pa ni /
NK125(co)002:21: mnyan yod kyi khyim bdag legs pa rab sad kyi
NK125(co)002:22: bu gser gyi glang po che dang lhan cig skyes
NK125(co)002:23: pa / rang gi glang po'i mche ba zur snga
NK125(co)002:24: phyir rgyal po gsal rgyal la phul bas de'i bu
NK125(co)002:25: mo chos gos can byin pa de yin la /
NK125(co)002:26: phyis khyo shug gnyis ka rab tu byung nas dgra bcom pa thob pa'o //
NK125(co)002:29: bcom ldan 'das yul ko sa la'i lo ma bdun
NK125(co)002:30: pa'i gnas su byon tshe der gnas seng ldeng nags
NK125(co)002:31: pa rab tu byung nas dgra bcom thob pa dben
NK125(co)002:32: par gnas pa'i mchog tu basngagasa pa de nyid do
NK125(co)002:34: nag po 'char ka'am dus ldan ni mnyan yod kyi
NK125(co)002:35: khyim bdag phyug po'i bu skyes dus sna ma'i me
NK125(co)002:36: tog gi char bab pas ngo mtshar zhing ston pa'i
NK125(co)002:37: zhabs 'bring du phul bas dgra bcom pa thob /
NK125(co)002:38: dur khrod du ro yi zas kyis 'tsho ba byas
NK125(co)002:39: pas nyams bzang zhing mdog smug nag tu 'gyur bas
NK125(co)002:40: dur khrod pa dang nag po chen por grags pa
NK125(co)002:41: chu len tshe nam mkha' la 'gro zhing chu bum
NK125(co)002:42: yang rjes su 'brang ba can de'o //
NK125(co)002:44: rdo rje mo'i bu ni bad sa'i rgyal po 'chang
NK125(co)002:45: byed rgyal por ma bskos pa'i dus su bram ze
NK125(co)002:46: rdo rje mo dang 'dus pa las chos gos 'dra
NK125(co)002:47: ba'i phru mas g.yogs te btsas pa mas sangs rgyas
NK125(co)002:48: la phul bas dgra bcom pa thob pa'o //
NK125(co)002:49: b+ha drah rgyal po zas gtsang gi khol po ral
NK125(co)002:50: bzang gi bu bcom ldan 'das la phul ba dgra
NK125(co)002:52: ka na ka batasahgasera be'u ni /
NK125(co)002:53: ma ga d+ha'i khyim bdag gcig gi bu btsas ma
NK125(co)002:54: thag tu gser gyi glang po che'i phru gu gcin
NK125(co)002:55: rtug gser du 'gyur ba zhig kyang btsas pas de'i
NK125(co)002:56: ming glang skyong ngam gser dbang ngam gser be'ura btags
NK125(co)002:57: / ma skyes dgras de'i glang po phrogs kyang ma
NK125(co)002:58: btub pa de rab tu byung nas dgra bcom thob
NK125(co)002:59: / pa'o // b+ha ra d+ha dza hi ra n+yam /
NK125(co)002:60: b+ha ra d+h+aa dza gser can mchog ni /
NK125(co)002:61: mnyan yod na khyim bdag b+ha ra d+h+aa dza'i rigs su gyur pa zhig gi bu /
NK125(co)002:62: lag pa gnyis gser gyi tong tses mtshan par skyes pa /
NK125(co)002:63: lag pa'i tong tse mi zad pas khyim gang bas
NK125(co)002:64: gser can mchog dang gser dbyig kyang zer bas de
NK125(co)002:65: nyid rab tu byung ste dgra bcom pa thob pa'o
NK125(co)002:66: // bag ku lah skad sor bzhag la shing shun can yang zer te /
NK125(co)002:67: mnyan yod kyi bram ze zhig gi bu rig byed
NK125(co)002:68: byang ba de pha ma shi nas ril gnas te
NK125(co)002:70: bcom ldan 'das de phyogs su byon pa'i tshe lhag
NK125(co)002:71: par dad pas ri las mchongs pa ston pa'i rdzu
NK125(co)002:72: 'phrul gyis blangs nas chos bstan pas dgra bcom pa
NK125(co)002:73: thob pa'o // ts+au d+aa pa r+aa kah lam phran bstan dang /
NK125(co)002:75: lam chen bstan gnyis spun yin te /
NK125(co)002:76: mnyan yod du bram ze mo gcig la bu skyes
NK125(co)002:77: tshad shi ba bud med rgan mo zhig gis bslab
NK125(co)002:79: lam phran bstan lo gsum lon dus lus ras dkar gyis dril te sdong bu'i tshul du byas /
NK125(co)002:80: snod mar khus bkang ba bu mo zhig la bskur nas /
NK125(co)002:81: sangs rgyas byon pa'i lam khar mgo yi ras la
NK125(co)002:82: me sbar te khyod khye'u dang bcas pas phyag 'tshal
NK125(co)002:83: lo zhes brjod de phul cig byas pa ltar phul
NK125(co)002:84: bas sangs rgyas 'khor bcas kyis khye'u tshe ring bar
NK125(co)002:85: gyur cig ces gsungs pa'i mod la /
NK125(co)002:86: mgo bo'i me de nyid me tog dmar por gyur te 'chi bdag las thar ba /
NK125(co)002:87: slar yang pha mas blangs nas rig byed bslab tu
NK125(co)002:88: bcug pas phu bos thams cad shes pas lam chen
NK125(co)002:89: par grags / nu bos brjod na b+ha brjed pa
NK125(co)002:90: sogs blo rtul ba'i mthar gyur bas lam chung bar
NK125(co)002:91: par grags / grags / des rang blo zhan pa
NK125(co)002:92: la skyo nas sangs rgyas la zhus te rab tu
NK125(co)002:94: ston pas de la rdul spang ba dri ma spang
NK125(co)002:95: ba'i tshig gnyis bslab pa kha ton du bzung nas
NK125(co)002:96: de'i don bsam zhing shes nas dgra bcom pa thob
NK125(co)002:97: kyang / de sngar blo zhan pas ma dad de
NK125(co)002:98: 'tsho byed gzhon nus gdugs tshod la ma bos pa
NK125(co)002:99: kyang / dang / dge slong ma rnams kyis mkhan
NK125(co)002:100: por bskos kyang brnyas 'dod kyi khri ches mtho ba
NK125(co)002:101: kyang / dang / bshams pa'i tshe / lam chung
NK125(co)002:102: bas rdzu 'phrul ldan cing tshig gnyis kyi don rgya
NK125(co)002:103: cher bshad pas thams cad ngo mtshar thob ste sems
NK125(co)002:104: kyi mos pa bsgyur ba'i mchog tu basngagasa pa de
NK125(co)002:105: kyang / dang / bshams pa'i tshe / nyid do
NK125(co)002:106: // phu bo lam chen po la'ang pha mas khyod
NK125(co)002:107: 'tsho ba sangs rgyas kyi drin yin pas rab tu
NK125(co)002:108: byung shig ces bskul ba la dga' ba'i yid kyis
NK125(co)002:109: rab tu byung nas dgra bcom pa de nyid gnas
NK125(co)002:110: brtan lam chen bstan yin no //
NK125(co)002:113: rgyal po'i khab kyi mdun na 'don b+ha ra d+h+wa dza'i rigs can gyi bur skyes /
NK125(co)002:114: cod pan med pa'i rgyal srid can bsod nams ldan
NK125(co)002:115: pa yin yang sngon las kyi lhag mas ci zos
NK125(co)002:116: pa rdor gyur pa la skyobs ston pa'i drung nas
NK125(co)002:117: rab tu byung ba'i skad cig de la dgra bcom
NK125(co)002:118: pa thob / zas bsod snyoms 'ba' zhig spyod pas bsod snyoms len du grags /
NK125(co)002:119: skabs gcig rgyal po shar ba de phyogs 'ong pa la ldang ba sogs ma byas pas /
NK125(co)002:120: rgyal po khro nas 'di'i mgo bo chod ces smras te song /
NK125(co)002:121: slar yang der 'ongs pa la gom pa drug gis
NK125(co)002:122: bsus pas rgyal po mdangs nyams shing sa gas pas
NK125(co)002:123: skrag nas bzod par gsol zhing dad par gyur pas
NK125(co)002:124: mdzad pa de nyid yin no //
NK125(co)002:127: byang phyogs gseg ma'i grong gi rgyal po klu'i phyag
NK125(co)002:128: rgya zhes pas rgyal srid kyi phyir pha bsad pa
NK125(co)002:129: la 'gyod nas rgyal srid spangs te ston pa'i spyan
NK125(co)002:130: sngar sdig pa bshags shing byang chub kyi sems bskyed
NK125(co)002:131: / rab tu byung bar gnang ste bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK125(co)002:132: bsnyung bar gnas pas sdig pa dag cing dgra bcom
NK125(co)002:133: pa thob nas lha dang mi la chos ston par
NK125(co)002:135: go ba kah sbed byed dam ba lang skyong yang zer ba ni /
NK125(co)002:136: khyim bdag gi rigs kyi gtso bo la bu lnga
NK125(co)002:137: yod pa'i che ba grags pa zhes bya ba bud
NK125(co)002:138: med kyi tshogs kyi rol mos brtse zhing gnas pa
NK125(co)002:139: de / mtshan mo bud med rnams gnyid log pas
NK125(co)002:140: sgren mo lus tshugs zhig pa ro ltar gyur pa
NK125(co)002:141: mthong ba la sngon gyi dge rtsas dur khrod kyi
NK125(co)002:143: rin po che'i lham gyon nas mtshan mo phyir phyungs te bdag gtsos zhes smra zhing 'khyams pa las /
NK125(co)002:144: de bzhin gshegs pa dge bzang gi gtsug lag khang du bzhugs pa'i drung du /
NK125(co)002:145: 'bab chu gnod pa can gyi khar lham bzhag ste
NK125(co)002:146: brgal nas phyin pa la rgyal bas chos bstan pas
NK125(co)002:147: rgyan gyis brgyan cing stan de la 'dug bzhin dgra
NK125(co)002:149: rgyan gyis brgyan bzhin du yang chos skyod de /
NK125(co)002:150: zhes sogs tshig bcad gsungs shing dge slong gi dngos por gyur pa nyid do //
NK125(co)002:151: slar yang de'i nu bo rnams kyang rab tu byung
NK125(co)002:152: ste dgra bcom thob pa de lnga la nye ba'i
NK125(co)002:154: a b+he r+yah mi phyed pa ni rgyal po'i khab
NK125(co)002:155: kyi bad sa'i bram ze pi lin+d+rahste srung dbang zhes
NK125(co)002:156: pa'i bu rgyal ba'i drung nas rab tu byung zhing
NK125(co)002:157: dgra bcom thob pa la mtshan mi phyed par grags
NK125(co)002:158: / des chu bo gang ga la bzang mo sdod
NK125(co)002:159: cig ces smras pas mi 'bab par sdod pa dang
NK125(co)002:160: / / gzugs can snying pos zhabs 'bring du phul
NK125(co)002:161: ba rnams la chom rkun gyis 'tshe ba rdzu 'phrul
NK125(co)002:162: gyi ra bas bsrung bas rdzu 'phrul che bar grags
NK125(co)002:164: 'di dag mchims nam mkha' grags pas mdzad pa'i gnas
NK125(co)002:165: brtan gyi skyes rabs zhes pa de las mdor bsdus
NK125(co)002:167: gnas brtan de rnams kyi lo rgyus ci rigs mdo dang 'dul ba rnams gsal /
NK125(co)002:168: gnas brtan rnams kyi phyag mtshan dang /
NK125(co)002:169: phyag mtshan de dag mthong ba sogs kyi phan yon dang /
NK125(co)002:170: de rnams kyi 'khor dgra bcom pa'i grangs dang /
NK125(co)002:171: gnas gang na bzhugs pa dang /
NK125(co)002:172: rgya nag sogs su byon tshul dang /
NK125(co)002:173: gsol ba btab pa'i phan yon bcas yig cha der 'dug la /
NK125(co)002:174: de'i khungs ni byams pas lung bstan pa zhes klu
NK125(co)002:175: mes kyis rgya nag gi yig tshang las rnyed pa
NK125(co)002:176: dang / 'phags pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi rtogs pa brjod pa'i mdo zhes pa dang /
NK125(co)002:177: gnas brtan spyan drangs pa'i mdo zhes pa dang /
NK125(co)002:178: gnas brtan lung bstan pa'i mdo zhes pa snga phyir 'gyur ba rnams dang /
NK125(co)002:179: thang jus jum rgyal pos gnas brtan spyan drangs pa'i 'phrin yig sogs yin par bshad /
NK125(co)002:180: gnas brtan phyag mchod kyi 'don char yang 'khor dang phyag mtshan bzhugs gnas rnams gsal ba ltar ro //
NK125(co)002:181: gnas brtan lo rgyus rgyas par 'bri sems kyang dpe
NK125(co)002:182: ma 'byor bas 'di ni 'jam mgon mi pham rin
NK125(co)002:183: po che'i skad gnyis shan sbyar la don gyi rnam
NK125(co)002:184: thar cha tshang bar 'dug pa zur du phyung ste
